---
title: "Creating a dblink to Oracle"

---

You might want to use Oracle and PostgreSQL databases in a business environment. A typical evaluation scenario is to use an existing Oracle infrastructure for the front end and PostgreSQL for reporting purposes. This setup helps us evaluate PostgreSQL without risking the production environment.

